        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Monday, February 8, 2021 6:07:18 PM",
        "content": "As a result, any community could be seen as criss-crossed with relations of “individualistic communism,” one-to-one relations that operate, to varying intensities and degrees, on the basis of “from each according to their ability, to each according to their needs.”",
