        "location": "2278-2279",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Monday, February 8, 2021 10:15:26 PM",
        "content": "We can describe a simple formula here: a certain action, repeated, becomes customary; as a result, it comes to define the actor’s essential nature. Alternately, a person’s nature may be defined by how others have acted toward him in the past.",
