        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Wednesday, February 10, 2021 9:44:43 PM",
        "content": "A world without debt would revert to primordial chaos, a war of all against all; no one would feel the slightest responsibility for one another; the simple fact of being human would have no significance; we would all become isolated planets who couldn’t even be counted on to maintain our proper orbits.",
