        "page": 226,
        "location": "4043-4044",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Friday, February 12, 2021 10:06:03 PM",
        "content": "German legal theorist Rudolf von Jhering famously remarked that ancient Rome had conquered the world three times: the first time through its armies, the second through its religion, the third through its laws.",
