        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Wednesday, June 2, 2021 2:03:26 PM",
        "content": "The WTO now forms the core of the global economic governance system, together with the IMF (International Monetary Fund) – in charge of access to short-term finance – and the World Bank – in charge of longer-term investments.",
