        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Saturday, June 5, 2021 2:14:44 PM",
        "content": "Thus practically all of today’s rich countries used nationalistic policies (e.g., tariffs, subsidies, restrictions on foreign trade) to promote their infant industries, though the exact mix of policies used, as well as their timing and duration, differed across countries.",
        "type": "HIGHLIGHT"
