        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Sunday, June 6, 2021 1:29:37 PM",
        "content": "So, in the name of ‘levelling the playing field’, the Bad Samaritan rich nations have created a new international trading system that is rigged in their favour. They are preventing the poorer countries from using the tools of trade and industrial policies that they had themselves so effectively used in the past in order to promote their own economic development – not just tariffs and subsidies, but also regulation of foreign investment and ‘violation’ of foreign intellectual property rights,",
