        "location": "3387-3388",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Saturday, June 12, 2021 4:42:38 PM",
        "content": "the famous saying by the Brazilian archbishop of Olinda and Recife, Dom Hélder Câmara: ‘When I give food to the poor, they call me a saint. When I ask why the poor have no food, they call me a communist.’",
