        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Wednesday, July 7, 2021 4:48:26 PM",
        "content": "This was all part of Ríos Montt’s new strategy for fighting communism. “The guerrilla is the fish. The people are the sea,” he said. “If you cannot catch the fish, you have to drain the sea.”",
        "type": "HIGHLIGHT"
