        "bookTile": "Mastery",
        "page": 50,
        "location": "763-763",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Thursday, July 8, 2021 4:45:18 PM",
        "content": "“Just as a well-filled day brings blessed sleep, so a well-employed life brings a blessed death.”",
