        "page": 38,
        "location": "577-580",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Monday, September 27, 2021 2:57:00 PM",
        "content": "Explore/Exploit In English, the words “explore” and “exploit” come loaded with completely opposite connotations. But to a computer scientist, these words have much more specific and neutral meanings. Simply put, exploration is gathering information, and exploitation is using the information you have to get a known good result.",
