        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Tuesday, September 28, 2021 6:09:47 PM",
        "content": "As Neumann observes, “Look at fish, for example: the bigger one is the dominant one. It’s very simple.” And because it’s so simple, it’s peaceful. Unlike chickens and primates, fish make order without shedding blood.",
        "type": "HIGHLIGHT"
