        "location": "1510-1511",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Tuesday, September 28, 2021 6:11:57 PM",
        "content": "Much as we bemoan the daily rat race, the fact that it’s a race rather than a fight is a key part of what sets us apart from the monkeys, the chickens—and, for that matter, the rats.",
