        "page": 271,
        "location": "4151-4153",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Saturday, October 2, 2021 8:58:44 PM",
        "content": "I’m an optimist in the sense that I believe humans are noble and honorable, and some of them are really smart.… I have a somewhat more pessimistic view of people in groups. —STEVE JOBS",
