        "page": 29,
        "location": "432-433",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Tuesday, October 5, 2021 5:34:42 PM",
        "content": "It’s human nature. We have all been too quick to make up our minds and too slow to change them. And if we don’t examine how we make these mistakes, we will keep making them.",
