        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Wednesday, October 6, 2021 6:36:21 AM",
        "content": "In the actual contest, many people did work all the way down to 0, but 0 was not the right answer. It wasn’t even close to right. The average guess of all the contestants was 18.91, so the winning guess was 13. How did I get this so wrong? It wasn’t my logic, which was sound. I failed because I only looked at the problem from one perspective—the perspective of logic.",
