        "bookTile": "Think Again",
        "page": 63,
        "location": "962-963",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Thursday, October 21, 2021 3:23:17 PM",
        "content": "Jeff Bezos says. “If you don’t change your mind frequently, you’re going to be wrong a lot.”",
