        "location": "1124-1126",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Thursday, October 21, 2021 3:45:59 PM",
        "content": "We learn more from people who challenge our thought process than those who affirm our conclusions. Strong leaders engage their critics and make themselves stronger. Weak leaders silence their critics and make themselves weaker.",
