        "content": "If you can’t solve a problem, then there is an easier problem you can’t solve: find it. —George Polya When the going gets tough, creative problem solvers create an easier, simpler problem that they can solve. They resolve that easier issue thoroughly and then study that simple scenario with laser focus. Those insights often point the way to a resolution of the original difficult problem.",
