        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Thursday, June 2, 2022 9:42:15 PM",
        "content": "Consider a subject you wish to understand, and clear the clutter until you have isolated one essential ingredient. Each complicated issue has several possible core ideas. You are not seeking “the” essential idea; you are seeking just one—consider a subject and pare it down to one theme.",
        "type": "HIGHLIGHT"
