        "page": 503,
        "location": "7703-7705",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Saturday, February 18, 2023 10:24:29 PM",
        "content": "For our own people we must broadcast not only the facts but also copious and precise commentaries on their importance and significance. Good propaganda must be stimulating. Our stations must therefore go on talking about the drunkard Churchill and the criminal Roosevelt on every possible occasion.",
