        "page": 559,
        "location": "8557-8560",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Thursday, February 23, 2023 10:29:02 PM",
        "content": "Is there a more lovely consecration of love, pray, than the birth of a handsome babe, glowing with health? Although it is obvious to the eyes of any reasonable person that nature blesses the love of two beings by giving them a child, these sinister degenerates claim, if you please, that the status of a man or a woman depends on a sealed document given by the State—as if that were of any importance in comparison with the ties which unite two people in love!",
