        "location": "10338-10340",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Monday, February 27, 2023 10:12:39 PM",
        "content": "In judging any question connected with superstition, it must be remembered that, although an oracle’s prophecies may be wrong a hundred times (when they are promptly forgotten), it suffices for one prophecy to be fortuitously confirmed by subsequent events, for it to be believed, cherished and handed down from generation to generation.",
