        "location": "10713-10715",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Wednesday, March 1, 2023 9:28:04 PM",
        "content": "The Church has succeeded in striking a very pretty balance between life on earth and in the Hereafter. On earth, they say, the poor must remain poor and blessed, for in Heaven the earthly rich will get nothing; and the unfortunate poor on earth believe them!",
