        "location": "7824-7827",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Thursday, April 6, 2023 2:07:41 PM",
        "content": "If a person is always inclined to do wrong the moment the inducement is there and no external power restrains him, we call him bad. In accordance with our explanation of wrong, this means that such a man not only affirms the will-to-live as it appears in his own body, but in this affirmation goes so far as to deny the will that appears in other individuals.",
