        "page": 100,
        "location": "1534-1536",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Tuesday, April 18, 2023 9:32:16 PM",
        "content": "Perhaps our word “man” (manas) still expresses something of precisely this feeling of self-satisfaction: man designated himself as the creature that measures values, evaluates and measures, as the “valuating animal as such.”",
