        "location": "390-392",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Tuesday, May 2, 2023 8:27:16 PM",
        "content": "If, however, a person should regard even the emotions of hatred, envy, covetousness, and imperiousness as life-conditioning emotions, as factors which must be present, fundamentally and essentially, in the general economy of life (which must, therefore, be further developed if life is to be further developed), he will suffer from such a view of things as from sea-sickness.",
