        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Tuesday, May 30, 2023 9:28:38 PM",
        "content": "All evil which is dependent on strong will – and perhaps there is nothing evil without strength of will – is degenerating, in our tepid atmosphere, into virtue.… The few hypocrites I have known impersonated hypocrisy: they were, like virtually every tenth man nowadays, actors.",
