        "location": "3409-3411",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Friday, June 9, 2023 2:04:44 PM",
        "content": "Dreams.— Either we have no dreams or our dreams are interesting. We should learn to arrange our waking life the same way: nothing or interesting.",
