        "location": "3420-3422",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Friday, June 9, 2023 2:07:03 PM",
        "content": "To move the crowd.— Must not anyone who wants to move the crowd be an actor who impersonates himself? Must he not first translate himself into grotesque obviousness and then present his whole person and cause in this coarsened and simplified version?",
