        "bookTile": "The Gay Science",
        "page": 288,
        "location": "4690-4693",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Saturday, June 10, 2023 12:18:25 PM",
        "content": "This unconditional will to truth—what is it? Is it the will not to allow oneself to be deceived? Or is it the will not to deceive? For the will to truth could be interpreted in the second way, too—if only the special case “I do not want to deceive myself” is subsumed under the generalization “I do not want to deceive.” But why not deceive? But why not allow oneself to be deceived?",
        "type": "HIGHLIGHT"
