        "location": "2346-2348",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Saturday, July 22, 2023 8:01:32 AM",
        "content": "Socialists desire to produce a good life for the greatest number. If the enduring homeland of this good life, the perfect state, were really achieved, it would destroy the earth from which a man of great intellect, or any powerful individual grows: I mean great energy. When this state is achieved, mankind would have become too feeble to produce genius any longer.",
