        "location": "2622-2624",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Saturday, July 22, 2023 8:57:29 AM",
        "content": "Talent. In such a highly developed humanity as the present one, each man by nature has access to many talents. Each has inborn talent, but only a few have inherited and cultivated such a degree of toughness, endurance, and energy that they really become a talent, become what they are20-that is, release it in works and actions.",
