        "content": "Bait. “Every man has his price”4—that is not true. But every one has a bait into which he must bite. Thus, to win certain people to a matter, one need only paint it as human, noble, charitable, self-sacrificing—and what matter could not be painted thus? It is the sweet candy of their souls: others have another.",
