        "location": "3899-3900",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Saturday, July 22, 2023 3:16:17 PM",
        "content": "Origin of courage. The ordinary man is courageous and invulnerable like a hero when he does not see the danger, when he has no eyes for it. Conversely, the hero’s one vulnerable spot is on his back; that is, where he has no eyes.",
        "type": "HIGHLIGHT"
