        "page": 265,
        "location": "4059-4061",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Saturday, July 22, 2023 3:47:25 PM",
        "content": "Alienated from the present. There are great advantages in for once removing ourselves distinctly from our time and letting ourselves be driven from its shore back into the ocean of former world views. Looking at the coast from that perspective, we survey for the first time its entire shape, and when we near it again, we have the advantage of understanding it better on the whole than do those who have never left it.",
