        "location": "1014-1019",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Tuesday, September 5, 2023 1:07:13 PM",
        "content": "After thousands of years of error and confusion, I have had the good fortune and, still more, the honour to have rediscovered the way that leads to a ‘yes’ and a ‘no’. I teach that one must say ‘no’ to everything that weakens and exhausts. I teach that one must say ‘yes’ to everything that strengthens, promotes the accumulation of power and [increases] pride. So far, neither of them have been taught, but instead virtue, selflessness, compassion, even the negation of life itself. These are all the values of exhausted men.",
