        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Monday, September 18, 2023 12:12:02 PM",
        "content": "Thus does the highest evil belong to the highest good: but this latter is the creative.– Let us at least talk of this, you who are wisest, grim though it may be. Remaining silent is grimmer; all truths that are kept silent become toxic. And so let everything shatter that can shatter on our truths! There is many a house still to build!–",
