        "location": "4046-4051",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Monday, September 25, 2023 9:37:56 PM",
        "content": "There is an old delusion that is called good and evil. Around soothsayers and astrologers has the wheel of this delusion turned up to now. Once people believed in soothsayers and astrologers, and therefore they believed: ‘All is fate: you shall, for you must!’ Then again people mistrusted all soothsayers and astrologers: and therefore they believed: ‘All is freedom: you can, for you will!’ O my brothers, about stars and the future there has hitherto been only surmise, and not knowledge; and therefore about good and evil there has hitherto been only surmise, and not knowledge!",
