        "location": "367-367",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Monday, December 4, 2023 1:46:29 PM",
        "content": "A baby is rocked not to relieve it from that which causes it to cry, but to make it stop crying. We do the same with our conscience, when we stiﬂe its voice in order to please people. We do not calm our conscience, but atain what we seek for: we no longer hear its voice",
