        "content": "It is bad enough to lie to other people, but it is far worse to lie to oneself. It is harmful particularly for the reason that if you lie to others you may be exposed, but if you lie to yourself there is no one to expose you. Terefore take care not to lie to yourself, especially in the maters of faith",
