        "content": "The ability to remember the past and to imagine the future is given us only in order to enable us, guided by this or that consideration, to decide more correctly our actions in the present, and not to regret the past or build for the future. Man lives only in the present instant. Everything else is either gone or is uncertain of occurring.",
