        "content": "A wise man was asked: what is the most important thing? Who is the most important man? And what time of life is the most important? And the wise man replied: The most important thing in life is to love all people, for therein is the concern of every man's life. “The most important man is the one with whom you have dealings at the present moment, for you cannot know whether you will ever have dealings with any one else. “But the most important time is the present, for in that alone a man has power over himself",
