        "content": "When misfortunes befall you know that they are not due to what you have done, but to what you have thought. If we cannot restrain ourselves from commiting a deed which we know is evil, it is due to the fact only that we frst permited ourselves to think of this evil act and failed to restrain our thoughts. Strive not to think of the things which you believe to be evil.",
