        "content": "We are like the passengers upon some gigantic ship, whose master has a passenger list that is unknown to us and contains the destination of the passengers. Until we are put ashore what else can we do but obey the laws of the ship, live in peace, concord and love with our fellow travelers and thus spend the time alloted to us?",
