        "content": "Does transformation terrify you? Nothing is accomplished without change. Water can not be heated without a transformation of fuel. Nourishment is impossible without a transformation of food. Te whole of earthly existence is a transformation. Understand that the transformation which awaits you has the same meaning, that it also is necessary in the very nature of things.",
