        "content": "Jesus answered: “Do not speak so. If you are afraid of suﬀering and death for me, that shows that you do not think of what is godly, but only of what is human. In this life people who live for the Kingdom of God must suﬀer, because the world loves its own, and hates what is godly. Men of the world always have tormented those who fulflled the will of the Father.",
