        "location": "242-242",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Tuesday, March 5, 2024 9:53:45 PM",
        "content": "If one does not eat of a certain dish, he cannot appreciate its true taste. If one has never been a prisoner himself, he cannot speak of the real sufferings of imprisonment",
