        "page": 519,
        "location": "7948-7951",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Wednesday, March 27, 2024 11:33:57 AM",
        "content": "BIGGER CITIES, BETTER BRAINS The more numerous and the more abundant the civilization (population) in a city, the more luxurious is the life of its inhabitants in comparison with that (of the inhabitants) of a lesser city. —The Muslim historian, Ibn Khaldûn, The Muqaddimah (1377, Chapter 4)",
