        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Wednesday, April 3, 2024 9:03:00 PM",
        "content": "As young Scipio Nasica found to his cost, the success of the rich was a gift bestowed by the poor. The rich had to learn the lesson that they depended on the people as a whole.",
