        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Sunday, April 21, 2024 9:30:18 PM",
        "content": "The fanaticism with which the whole of Greek thought throws itself at rationality betrays a state of emergency: one was in peril, one had only one choice: either to perish or – be absurdly rational.…",
