        "location": "9941-9943",
        "dateOfCreation": "Added on Tuesday, May 14, 2024 1:04:06 PM",
        "content": "Nixon kept on urging Reagan to set up good-cop/bad-cop dynamics in his administration. “You need at least two or three nut-cutters who will take on the opposition so that you can take the high road,” Nixon wrote Reagan in November 1982.",
